.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, project-manager, writer, lawyer, social-worker, freelancer, designer
7 different games are played: domino, billiard, chess, whist, poker, monopoly, scrabble
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, tulip, orchid, aconite, amaryllis, daisy
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is the person playing whist##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the project-manager is the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person playing monopoly##2
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the writer is in the middle##1
11. the person who growslily is the social-worker##1
12. the social-worker is the person driving the bike##1
13. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing chess##1
14. the person playing monopoly is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
16. the project-manager is on the left of the freelancer##1
17. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing chess##1
18. the designer is on the right of the person playing poker##1
19. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
